Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.80,0:25:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H61AAF8&\3c&H041691&\b1}塔奇克侠{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.53,0:24:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马 通过吸收网络上的丢包
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.30,0:25:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变身为更加鲜艳的塔奇克侠
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.21,0:25:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在呼唤我…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.91,0:25:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超弦s！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.18,0:25:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定明年春天上映


